{"tid":666430,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"百萬石音樂祭2018","createTime":"2018-05-16T00:57:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T02:06:06.000Z","uid":86948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f13d12a97af52a39ccfe33aee177c9e2d505e912","tid":666430,"uid":86948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T00:57:48.000Z","msg":"作為日本最大LIVE FEST之一、北陸最大型LIVE FEST<br />\n喺金澤舉行嘅百萬石音樂祭今年個LINE UP真係可以話痴Q線<br />\n參戰ARTIST每一隊都係各據一方嘅霸者<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.millionrock.com/artist/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.millionrock.com%2Fartist%2F&d=LzJ%2Fgm2hnr%2FgeU7MD%2BfhFdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=8078a4ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.millionrock.com/artist/</a><br />\n<br />\n不論你係聽開重型音樂、定係POP ROCK都一定有野岩你聽<br />\n第二日嘅SiM、Crossfaith、coldrain 3兄弟同一日簡直令我想即時衝過去<br />\n仲要第一日嘅FALILV同Passcode電音Core兄妹團<br />\n<br />\n今年舉日行日期係6月2同3號<br />\n有冇巴絲打會去呀?<br />\n<br />\n我仲諗緊去唔去好....<br />\n又想去6月尾SiM嘅dead pop fest<br />\n但係依堆神LINE UP又好吸引<br />\n大家最想睇嘅又係邊隊?"},{"pid":"9804bc691243c3651d2b72b6aa88a872f2844d75","tid":666430,"uid":86948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T00:58:48.000Z","msg":"DAY1 TIMETABLE<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.millionrock.com/img/timetable/imgDay1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.millionrock.com%2Fimg%2Ftimetable%2FimgDay1.jpg&h=a43ec000&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDAY2 TIMETABLE<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.millionrock.com/img/timetable/imgDay2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.millionrock.com%2Fimg%2Ftimetable%2FimgDay2.jpg&h=2ab1c7e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6005b810ff92fbdf596ad761cfe27af0134b9b68","tid":666430,"uid":151354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T16:07:00.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a584c5ad28c43585f26ee8892df05bda825c14c8","tid":666430,"uid":86948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0